53
00:03:01,395 --> 00:03:03,395
Hey, Joon Hyung. Hey!

54
00:03:04,925 --> 00:03:07,795
Gosh, where is he rushing so much to?

55
00:03:07,795 --> 00:03:08,925
Did something good happen?

56
