66
00:03:49,455 --> 00:03:50,725
Hello? This is Kim Dae Ho.

67
00:03:51,395 --> 00:03:54,725
Hello, Mr. Kim? This is Jeong Joon Hyung, Bok Joo's friend.

68
00:03:55,155 --> 00:03:57,395
Oh, you're Bok Joo's future husband.

69
