91
00:05:05,895 --> 00:05:08,165
Don't you tell Bok Joo about this. Do you hear me?

92
00:05:09,165 --> 00:05:10,895
She'll have a match soon. If she finds out,

93
00:05:11,195 --> 00:05:12,625
she won't focus on her training.

94
00:05:12,795 --> 00:05:14,395
She worked so hard to make the national team.

95
00:05:14,895 --> 00:05:18,165
Okay. I promise you I will keep that in mind.

96
00:05:27,525 --> 00:05:28,525
Yes, Bok...

97
00:05:29,595 --> 00:05:32,525
I'm training right now, so I'll call you back when I'm done. Okay.

98
00:05:34,755 --> 00:05:37,995
What's going on? He fell asleep last night, and now this?

99
00:05:39,655 --> 00:05:41,295
I wanted to hear his voice.

100
00:05:45,525 --> 00:05:47,125
What is it? Didn't your boyfriend pick up?

101
00:05:47,725 --> 00:05:50,725
What? He did, but he said he will call me back later.

102
00:05:52,125 --> 00:05:54,295
I didn't know you had a boyfriend. Show us his picture.

103
00:05:54,655 --> 00:05:55,695
Let's see what he looks like.

104
00:05:59,395 --> 00:06:00,395
Here.

105
00:06:02,625 --> 00:06:04,825
Hey. Are you really saying he's your boyfriend?

106
00:06:04,825 --> 00:06:07,355
Don't lie to us. You got these pictures from the internet, right?

107
00:06:07,855 --> 00:06:09,555
No. He's in my school's swimming team.

108
00:06:09,555 --> 00:06:11,695
Maybe you did something great in your previous life.

109
00:06:11,695 --> 00:06:14,555
He's so handsome. It's like she won a lottery.

110
00:06:14,555 --> 00:06:16,855
But apparently, she can't get her handsome boyfriend...

111
00:06:16,855 --> 00:06:18,055
on the phone.

112
00:06:18,925 --> 00:06:20,995
That's not a good sign.

113
00:06:20,995 --> 00:06:23,025
I think you two are going to break up soon.

114
00:06:24,355 --> 00:06:26,795
- What? 
- 90 percent of the athletes who...

115
00:06:26,795 --> 00:06:28,125
have a girlfriend or a boyfriend...

116
00:06:28,125 --> 00:06:31,055
go through a breakup after coming here.

117
00:06:31,295 --> 00:06:32,455
But there're stages.

118
00:06:32,855 --> 00:06:35,525
At first, it gets harder to get him on the phone.

119
00:06:35,525 --> 00:06:38,125
He either ignores your call, or says he'll call back later. Then,

120
00:06:38,355 --> 00:06:41,125
he will sound aloof, and his answers will be very short.

121
00:06:41,125 --> 00:06:43,825
And finally, he will drop the bomb.

122
00:06:44,325 --> 00:06:46,395
"I'm sorry. I think we should break up."

123
00:06:46,595 --> 00:06:48,155
"I'm seeing someone else."

124
00:06:51,425 --> 00:06:53,655
No way. He's just training right now, so...

125
00:06:54,655 --> 00:06:56,155
- Gosh, I'm sorry. 
- Hey.

126
00:06:56,155 --> 00:06:58,525
He's not training. It's lunch time.

127
00:06:58,525 --> 00:06:59,695
We went to a sports university, too.

128
00:07:01,155 --> 00:07:03,225
With your boyfriend's looks,

129
00:07:03,825 --> 00:07:05,455
I'll give it a month at the longest.

130
00:07:05,455 --> 00:07:07,955
Girls would never leave him alone. Am I right?

131
00:07:10,525 --> 00:07:11,955
Seon Ok, Tae Kwon.

132
00:07:11,955 --> 00:07:13,625
- The hot dogs are here. 
- What took you so long?

133
00:07:14,555 --> 00:07:16,995
I brought hot dogs. There's no ketchup.

134
00:07:16,995 --> 00:07:19,825
- Why? You have no tact at all. 
- They didn't have it.

135
00:07:22,725 --> 00:07:26,025
The food tastes so much better now that you're filling in for Bok Joo.

136
00:07:26,495 --> 00:07:28,925
Tae Kwon. I'll have you as our new member. Okay?

137
00:07:28,925 --> 00:07:31,225
Sure. I'll be honored. Count me in.

138
00:07:31,225 --> 00:07:34,295
Okay. We're now the new trio.

139
00:07:36,525 --> 00:07:38,395
- It's our former member. 
- It's Bok Joo.

140
00:07:39,125 --> 00:07:41,725
Hey, Bok Joo. You're calling me in a very long time.

141
00:07:41,725 --> 00:07:43,325
I almost forget how your voice sounded.

142
00:07:44,325 --> 00:07:46,295
That's why I'm calling you now.

143
00:07:46,695 --> 00:07:47,755
How are you, Nan Hee?

144
00:07:48,255 --> 00:07:49,325
Where's Seon Ok?

145
00:07:49,325 --> 00:07:51,695
She's next to me. We're eating snacks.

146
00:07:51,955 --> 00:07:52,955
Have you eaten?

147
00:07:53,395 --> 00:07:54,855
Have you talked to your boyfriend?

148
00:07:55,525 --> 00:07:58,125
No, I haven't. He's in training.

149
00:07:58,495 --> 00:08:00,595
What? Joon Hyung is in training?

150
00:08:05,895 --> 00:08:06,995
What happened?

151
00:08:07,055 --> 00:08:09,995
Where did Joon Hyung go after lying to Bok Joo?

152
00:08:10,055 --> 00:08:12,755
I have no idea. He said he had to go somewhere.

153
00:08:12,755 --> 00:08:15,955
What is Joon Hyung up to these days?

154
00:08:15,955 --> 00:08:18,625
Do you also suspect that he's with another woman?

155
00:08:18,995 --> 00:08:22,155
I don't want to suspect him, but that's the feeling I get.

156
00:08:22,695 --> 00:08:24,155
What else could it be other than women?

157
00:08:24,795 --> 00:08:26,655
Listen, Joon Hyung tends to have...

158
00:08:26,655 --> 00:08:28,555
many women around him,

159
00:08:28,555 --> 00:08:30,555
but he's not the type to betray.

160
00:08:31,125 --> 00:08:32,295
How do you know that?

161
00:08:32,625 --> 00:08:34,725
As a man, I can't guarantee it.

162
00:08:34,995 --> 00:08:36,025
Forget it.

163
00:08:36,595 --> 00:08:38,355
We need evidence to catch him...

164
00:08:38,355 --> 00:08:40,725
or to straighten out any misunderstanding.

165
00:08:41,265 --> 00:08:44,655
Tae Kwon, we need your cooperation.

166
00:08:48,495 --> 00:08:49,525
Hey.

167
00:08:50,325 --> 00:08:51,625
My niece's future husband.

168
00:08:52,855 --> 00:08:54,955
I'm not sure if I can ask this,

169
00:08:55,295 --> 00:08:57,955
but can you come for two hours tomorrow?

170
00:08:58,625 --> 00:09:00,225
My girlfriend is very upset right now.

171
00:09:00,425 --> 00:09:01,655
Okay, I will.

172
00:09:02,195 --> 00:09:04,155
I'll come after my training.

173
00:09:09,655 --> 00:09:10,725
Could you let me go?

174
00:09:15,265 --> 00:09:17,155
- Hello, Honey? 
- Aren't you coming?

175
00:09:17,425 --> 00:09:20,495
